<i>Illegal miners dump nearly
30 tons of this heavy metal</i>

00:10:01.900 --> 00:10:04.470
<i>into Peruvian rivers every year.</i>

00:10:05.404 --> 00:10:09.541
<i>And a recent study found that
many people in local communities</i>

00:10:09.541 --> 00:10:11.510
<i> had mercury
 levels in their bodies</i>

00:10:11.510 --> 00:10:13.779
<i>five times the safe limit.</i>

