And somewhere in there,
there's a whole lot of gold.

00:10:21.386 --> 00:10:23.089
But, I can't see any.

00:10:25.691 --> 00:10:28.960
So, that's the image I took of
that guy while he was doing--

00:10:28.960 --> 00:10:31.830
<i> He stirred that mercury
with his feet for an hour.</i>

00:10:31.830 --> 00:10:34.399
<i>When you do that, you realize,
 these guys aren't rich.</i>

00:10:34.399 --> 00:10:36.802
Okay. The bad guys aren't rich.
The gold miners aren't--

00:10:36.802 --> 00:10:38.904
No one's getting rich
off this at all.

00:10:38.904 --> 00:10:41.173
It's actually the reverse.

00:10:41.173 --> 00:10:43.142
This guy wanted to
go to university.

00:10:43.142 --> 00:10:46.244
He'd gone to become a gold miner
to save up for university.

00:10:46.244 --> 00:10:47.780
He was never gonna
go to university.

00:10:47.780 --> 00:10:49.582
He was poisoning
himself to death.

00:10:50.382 --> 00:10:53.285
He hadn't been paid
for two weeks.

00:10:53.285 --> 00:10:54.820
The other two workers
that worked there

00:10:54.820 --> 00:10:57.022
hadn't been paid
for three months.

00:10:57.956 --> 00:11:02.294
And what I saw was this endless
poverty cycle, this trap.

00:11:02.294 --> 00:11:04.929
People stuck in
this poverty trap

00:11:04.929 --> 00:11:05.964
that they couldn't get out of.

00:11:05.964 --> 00:11:08.500
The longer they worked
and not got paid

00:11:08.500 --> 00:11:10.569
the more they were
committed to work.

00:11:10.569 --> 00:11:13.639
<i>So it was all really just
 miserable and tragic.</i>

00:11:13.639 --> 00:11:17.343
<i>This was where we got our water
from and washed every day.</i>

00:11:17.343 --> 00:11:18.744
<i>This is a mercury tailings</i>

00:11:18.744 --> 00:11:21.279
<i>a sort of gold mining tailings
 pond full of mercury.</i>

00:11:21.680 --> 00:11:23.282
So, it makes you realize that

00:11:23.282 --> 00:11:25.418
these guys aren't
doing that for fun.

00:11:26.217 --> 00:11:28.687
This idea of these nasty people

00:11:28.687 --> 00:11:30.722
destroying the Amazon,
they're not.

00:11:30.722 --> 00:11:32.692
They're just people
trying to make a living.

